:
"Output in TSV format (default when stdout is not a terminal)"
}
}
,
"--app"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动交互式应用，可选择任务并预览、继续执行、调整或删除"
,
"en"
:
"Launch interactive app to select, preview, iterate, adjust, or delete tasks"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有任务（终端下进入交互选择，非终端下输出 TSV）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all tasks (interactive app in terminal, TSV otherwise)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --active"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 只显示活跃任务（有 TODO.md）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show only active tasks (with TODO.md)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --completed"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 只显示已完成任务（有 DONE.md）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show only completed tasks (with DONE.md)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --csv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: CSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Output in CSV format"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --active --tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 活跃任务以 TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show active tasks in TSV format"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent job ls --app"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 强制进入交互式应用模式，选择任务后可预览/继续/调整/删除"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Force interactive app mode to select, preview, iterate, adjust, or delete tasks"
}
]
}
